Date:6/15/2004 11:35:51 AM
From:Paul Senior
I'm still holding my few shares of AUO (and GNSS too).

My unsupported-by-facts guess is that AUO is a well-known Chinese stock in a
rapidly growing subsector that supplies popular products to the masses, and so
this stock attracts the gambling instinct of Chinese traders. Hence the
volatility as the punters take (or lose)profits based on trading trends they
see.

I remain positive about the company prospects and its market, although I'm no
expert.
